   in n + 1 indeterminates 
  
    
      
        
          x
          
            0
          
        
        ,
        …
        ,
        
          x
          
            n
          
        
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{0},\ldots ,x_{n},}
   the U-resultant is the resultant of 
  
    
      
        
          f
          
            1
          
        
        ,
        …
        ,
        
          f
          
            n
          
        
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle f_{1},\ldots ,f_{n},}
   and 
  
    
      
        
          U
          
            0
          
        
        
          x
          
